<h1><strong>Tobacco Taxes</strong></h1>
<p>High  taxes on tobacco products are a proven way to reduce tobacco use especially  among youth. The current federal cigarette tax is $1.01 per pack, and the  current average state cigarette tax is $1.46 per pack. Illinois is the only state that has increased itstheir cigarette taxes in 2012 so&nbsp;far.</p>
